{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775895481012,"sessionID":"ses_28461db48ffeMJOvl72ZnwHnVc","part":{"id":"prt_d7b9e7e91001nMcs7FDRZ3UOD0","messageID":"msg_d7b9e6610001lZScx1tKfa3Ltn","sessionID":"ses_28461db48ffeMJOvl72ZnwHnVc","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-024: DockerService 封装 — Design Document\n2: \n3: ## Architecture\n4: \n5: ### Component Diagram\n6: ```\n7: ┌─────────────────┐\n8: │   CLI Commands  │\n9: │  (deploy, etc)  │\n10: └────────┬────────┘\n11:          │\n12: ┌────────▼────────┐\n13: │  DockerService  │\n14: │ (docker_service)│\n15: └────────┬────────┘\n16:          │\n17:     ┌────┴────┐\n18:     ▼         ▼\n19: ┌───────┐ ┌───────┐\n20: │Docker │ │Docker │\n21: │ SDK   │ │ CLI   │\n22: └───┬───┘ └───────┘\n23:     │\n24:     ▼\n25: ┌─────────┐\n26: │ Docker  │\n27: │ Daemon  │\n28: └─────────┘\n29: ```\n30: \n31: ## Key Design Decisions\n32: \n33: ### Dual Backend Strategy\n34: - Primary: Docker SDK for Python (docker-py)\n35: - Fallback: Docker CLI subprocess calls\n36: - Automatic detection of available backend\n37: \n38: ### Connection Management\n39: - Support for local Docker socket (unix:///var/run/docker.sock)\n40: - Support for remote Docker daemon via env variables\n41: - Connection pooling for SDK backend\n42: \n43: ### Error Handling\n44: - Custom exception hierarchy for Docker-specific errors\n45: - Structured error messages with actionable suggestions\n46: - Retry logic for transient failures\n47: \n48: ### Async Support\n49: - Async methods for long-running operations (pull, build)\n50: - Callback-based progress reporting\n51: - Timeout configuration per operation\n52: \n53: ## Data Flow\n54: 1. CLI command calls DockerService method\n55: 2. Service validates parameters\n56: 3. Execute via SDK or CLI backend\n57: 4. Parse and structure response\n58: 5. Return result or raise exception\n\n(End of file - total 58 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-024: DockerService 封装 — Design Document\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Component Diagram\n```\n┌─────────────────┐\n│   CLI Commands  │\n│  (deploy, etc)  │\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n┌────────▼────────┐\n│  DockerService  │\n│ (docker_service)│\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n    ┌────┴────┐\n    ▼         ▼\n┌───────┐ ┌───────┐\n│Docker │ │Docker │","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/design.md","time":{"start":1775895480979,"end":1775895481011}}}}
